            <h1 id="whatis">What is WeChat?</h1>
            <p>Tencent's WeChat, also known as Weixin in Chinese, is a Chinese instant messaging, social media, and mobile payment app.<br>WeChat supports text messaging, voice messaging on hold, broadcast (one-to-many) messaging, video conferencing,<Br> video games, mobile payment, photo and video sharing, and location sharing.</p>
            <p>Some requirements before you start, ensure that you have the following requirements!</p>
            <ol>
              <li>A Smartphone</li>
              <li><b>A Valid Phone Number</b> linked to your Smartphone. </li>
              <li>A sufficient mobile phone storage!</li>
            </ol>
          <h2 id="install">Installation Guide</h2>
          <p>Click on your preferred device to download the application!<br>Please select <b>Get it on Google Play if you're an Android User</b>, otherwise <b>select Download on the App Store for IPhone Users.</b></p>
          <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tencent.mm&pcampaignid=web_share"><img src="/images/For-Logos/to_google_play_store.png" width="180" height="70"></a>
          <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/wechat/id414478124"><img src="/images/For-Logos/to_apple_store.png" width="180" height="60"></a>
          <p>1. Once Installation is done, Open the application and select Sign Up</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-1.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">
          <p>2. Press Sign up Via Mobile</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-2.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">
          <p>3. Enter Details such as Name, Select the country region you reside in & <br>must be linked to ur phone number, then lastly create the password</p>
          <p>click I have read and accept WeChat's Terms of Service, then Accept and Continue.</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-3.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">
          <p>4. Optional:Read Wechat Privacy Policy by scrolling, otherwise <Br>click I have read and accept the above terms and click Next.</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-4.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">
          <p>5. Press Start to start Security Verification, afterwards solve the puzzle</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-5.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">
          <p>6.Enter Verification Code sent to your mobile phone.</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-6.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">
          <p>7. Click I have read and understand the above</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-7.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">
          <p>8. Click I have read and acknowledge the privacy policy</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-8.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">
          <p>9. You are redirected to the homepage! It is completed!</p>
          <img src="/images/WeChat/we-9.jpg" width="300px" srcset="">


