          <button class="collapsible">About WeChat</button>
          <div class="content">
            <p>What is WeChat?
                As of the third quarter of 2018, WeChat had over 1.08 billion monthly active user accounts, making it one of the most influential mobile products worldwide. <br><br>WeChat began as a chat app and has since developed into a market-leading platform that links individuals, companies, and services in China and worldwide.
                
                What is the Official Account on WeChat?<br><br>
                WeChat Official Accounts are a new service designed for businesses, celebrities, government agencies, and organizations. Millions of users can be reached by using official accounts to promote brands. In addition to being a necessary tool for connecting with customers, vendors must have an official WeChat account in order to apply for the WeChat Pay service.</p>
          </div>
          <button class="collapsible">About WeChat Pay</button>
          <div class="content">
            <p>TWith the help of the WeChat app's integrated payment feature, WeChat Pay, users can quickly complete payments using their smartphones. <br><br>WeChat offers a variety of payment options, including Quick Pay, QR Code Payments, In-App Web-Based Payments, and Native In-App Payments, to accommodate your customers' diverse needs and meet their various payment needs.  <br><br> When used in conjunction with WeChat official accounts, the WeChat Pay service investigates and enhances the o2o consumption experience and offers qualified internet solutions for brick-and-mortar businesses. It is the best choice of mobile payments.</p>
          </div>
